body:
Currently regular POJO-valued properties allow usage like this:

```
class Info {
  public int publicId;
  public long internalId;
}

class Person {
  @JsonIgnoreProperties({ "internalId" })
  public Info info;
}
```

but not

```
class PersonInline {
  @JsonUnwrapped
  @JsonIgnoreProperties({ "internalId" })
  public Info info;
}
```

This usage should, however, work. And same for `@JsonIncludeProperties`.

**NOTE**: first task is to see if this might already work (or not)

