```
 @Data
    static class SerTest {
        String a;
        String b;
    }
static void test() {
  SerTest serTest = new SerTest();
        serTest.setA("aaaaaaa");
System.out.println(
        JsonMapper.builder()
                .configure(JsonNodeFeature.WRITE_NULL_PROPERTIES, false)
                        .build().writeValueAsString(serTest));
}
```
expected output :  {"a": "aaaaaaa"}
produced:  {"a":"aaaaaaa","b":null}
# Version
3.1.0 ~3.1.2

# Other Tries
```
System.out.println(jsonMapperBuilder
                .disable(JsonNodeFeature.WRITE_NULL_PROPERTIES)
                .build().writeValueAsString(serTest));
```
result :  not effected 
