                    .enable(StreamWriteFeature.WRITE_BIGDECIMAL_AS_PLAIN)
                    .build()).build();

    BigDecimal bigDecimal = new BigDecimal(100);
    String directAsString = mapper.writeValueAsString(bigDecimal);
    String throughNode = mapper.writeValueAsString(mapper.valueToTree(bigDecimal));
    assertEquals(directAsString, throughNode);

    mapper = JsonMapper.builder(JsonFactory.builder().build())
            .disable(JsonNodeFeature.STRIP_TRAILING_BIGDECIMAL_ZEROES).build();

